ksdk:manifest.name: FRDM-K28F
ksdk:manifest.brief: This is SDK version 2.5.0 manifest file. It describes the content of the FRDM-K28F and additional settings for tools that support SDK version 2.5.0

board.name: FRDM-K28F
board.description: The NXP FRDM-K28F is a development board for the Kinetis K28F MCU.

device.name: MK28F15
device.description: K28F: Kinetis® K28F 150 MHz, 1 MB SRAM Microcontrollers (MCUs) based on ARM® Cortex®-M4 Core

specific.content: The Kinetis K28F is a high performance 150 MHz ARM® Cortex®-M4 with FPU Microcontroller (MCU) which integrates 2 MB of embedded Flash, 1 MB of SRAM, dual.USB controllers (High-Speed and Full-Speed), an SDRAM controller, a QuadSPI interface and Power Management Unit with Core Voltage Bypass.
